# B-10 repro per Austin's recipe: fresh session, warm a DISTANT start
# pose (its horizon fills the cache with planet-scale coarse ancestors),
# then teleport straight to the site and raw-shot the first frames.
# Run with TRI_RAW_CAPTURE=1.
mode fly
weather time 322
teleport 0.0 0.0 0.5
look 0 -30
bench 20
teleport -38.516 -104.457 0.33
look -168 -58
shot gb_frame1
bench 1
shot gb_frame2
bench 2
shot gb_frame4
bench 4
shot gb_frame8
bench 30
shot gb_settled
